# How to Create SQL Database Using Commands

**SHOW DATABASES;**
_Show all databases_

**SHOW TABLES;**
_Show all tables in the selected database_

**CREATE DATABASE database_name;**
_Create a new database_

**USE database_name;**
_Select and use a specific database_

**CREATE TABLE table_name (column1 datatype, column2 datatype, column3 datatype);**
_Create a new table with specified columns and data types_

**INSERT INTO table_name VALUES (value1, value2, value3);**
_Insert values into a table_

**SELECT * FROM table_name;**
_Display all records from a table_


